'''無齒鰺'''（学名：''Gnathanodon speciosus''），又稱'''黃金鰺'''、'''黃鸝無齒鰺'''，俗名為虎斑瓜，為[[輻鰭魚綱|輻鰭魚綱]][[鱸形目|鱸形目]][[鱸亞目|鱸亞目]][[鰺科|鰺科]]的其中一個[[種|種]]。其[[种加词|种加词]]“''speciosus''”意为“好看的”、“艳丽的”。

==分類及命名==
[[File:Silver_&_Gold.jpg|thumb]]優游的無齒鰺]]
本魚最早由[[瑞典|瑞典]][[博物學|博物學]]家彼得·福斯克斯（PeterForsskål）於1775年首次對這一物種進行了科學描述。<ref name = "Zoocat">{{cite book | last = Hosese | first = D.F. |author2=Bray, D.J. |author3=Paxton, J.R. |author4=Alen, G.R. | title = Zoological Catalogue of Australia Vol. 35 (2) Fishes | publisher = CSIRO | year = 2007 | location = Sydney | pages = 1150 | isbn =978-0-643-09334-8 }}</ref>將該物種稱為''Scomber''屬，該物種最初被稱為兩個名稱，即''Scomber rim''及''Scomber speciosus''，並將「rim」作為該物種的阿拉伯名稱的轉錄。<ref name="Forsskal">{{cite book|last=Forsskål|first=P.S.|title=Descriptiones Animalium Avium, Amphibiorum, Piscium, Insectorum, Vermium|year=1775|pages=54–56|editor=Niebuh, C|url=https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/2087954|language=la|accessdate=2011-01-16|archive-date=2019-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190827101606/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/2087954|dead-url=no}}</ref>因此，當局將''Scomber rim''視為初級同義詞。<ref name="cat">{{cite web|last=California Academy of Sciences: Ichthyology |title=Catalog of Fishes |publisher=CAS |date=September 2009 |url=http://researcharchive.calacademy.org/research/ichthyology/catalog/fishcatmain.asp |accessdate=2011-01-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150503081145/http://researcharchive.calacademy.org/research/ichthyology/catalog/fishcatmain.asp |archivedate=2015-05-03 |df= }}</ref>在[[荷蘭|荷蘭]][[魚類學|魚類學]]家Pieter Bleeker將它放入''Gnathanodon''屬之前，本種被轉移到''Caranx''屬，這個名字來源於拉丁語中的「無牙頜」。除了Forsskål的命名之外，其他七個後來的名字也被歸為魚類，所有這些名字現在都被認為是ICZN規則下的無效初級同義詞。
== 分布 ==
本魚分布於[[印度|印度]][[太平洋|太平洋]]區，包括[[紅海|紅海]]、[[東非|東非]]、[[馬爾地夫|馬爾地夫]]、[[斯里蘭卡|斯里蘭卡]]、[[印度|印度]]、[[孟加拉灣|孟加拉灣]]、[[泰國|泰國]]、[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]、[[印尼|印尼]]、[[日本|日本]]、[[台灣|台灣]]、[[中國|中國]]、[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]、[[澳洲|澳洲]]、[[新幾內亞|新幾內亞]]、[[所羅門群島|所羅門群島]]、[[密克羅尼西亞|密克羅尼西亞]]、[[馬紹爾群島|馬紹爾群島]]、[[馬里亞納群島|馬里亞納群島]]、[[斐濟群島|斐濟群島]]、[[諾魯|諾魯]]、[[吐瓦魯|吐瓦魯]]、[[夏威夷群島|夏威夷群島]]、[[薩摩亞群島|薩摩亞群島]]、[[吉里巴斯|吉里巴斯]]、[[法屬波里尼西亞|法屬波里尼西亞]]、[[美國|美國]][[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]、[[加利福尼亞灣|加利福尼亞灣]]、[[加拉巴哥群島|加拉巴哥群島]]、[[厄瓜多|厄瓜多]]、[[巴拿馬|巴拿馬]]沿岸海域。

== 深度 ==
水深0至20公尺。

== 特徵 ==
本魚體呈橢圓形且側扁，背側輪廓比腹側輪廓略微凸起，特別是在前面。<ref name = "FAO_CP">{{cite book |last= Smith-Vaniz |first= W.|editor= Carpenter, K.E. |editor2=Niem, V.H. |title= The Living Marine Resources of the Western Central Pacific Vol 4. Bony fishes part 2 (Mugilidae to Carangidae)|url= ftp://ftp.fao.org/docrep/fao/009/y4160e/y4160e00.pdf|format= PDF|series= FAO species identification guide for fishery purposes |year= 1999|publisher= FAO|location= Rome|isbn= 92-5-104301-9|pages= 2659–2757|chapter= Carangidae|accessdate=2011-01-16}}</ref>下頜、鋤骨均無齒，僅舌面粗糙。體黃色，兩側有9至11條寬窄不一的黑色橫帶，隨著魚的生長，身體逐漸變成銀色，橫帶逐漸消失被深色斑點所取代，背鰭硬棘8枚、背鰭軟條18-20枚、臀鰭硬棘3枚、臀鰭軟條15-17枚，體長可達110公分，體重可達15公斤。<ref name = "Oman">{{cite book | last = Randall | first = John E. | title = Coastal Fishes of Oman | year = 1995 | location = Honolulu | page = 183 | isbn = 0-8248-1808-3 | publisher = University of Hawaiʻi Press | others = University of Hawaii Press }}</ref><ref name="Pepperel2010">{{cite book|last=Pepperel|first=J.|title=Fishes of the Open Ocean: A Natural History and Illustrated Guide|url=https://archive.org/details/fishesofopenocea00juli|year=2010|publisher=University Of Chicago Press|isbn=978-0-226-65539-0|page=[https://archive.org/details/fishesofopenocea00juli/page/n279 272]}}</ref>

== 生態 ==
本魚主要棲息於珊瑚礁區，成群活動，偶而也會進入岩石海岸及港口防波堤內，會跟隨在大型魚類後方，如鯊魚、石斑魚，甚至[[水母|水母]]。<ref name = "Hawaii">{{cite book | last = Honebrink | first = Randy R. | year = 2000 | title = A Review of the Biology of the Family Carangidae, with Emphasis on Species Found in Hawaiian Waters | location = Honolulu | publisher = Hawaii Department of Land and Natural Resources | series = Division of Aquatic Resources Technical Report, 20-01 | page = 17 | url = http://hawaii.gov/dlnr/dar/pubs/ulua01.pdf | accessdate = 2011-01-16 | archive-date = 2012-03-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120320011628/http://hawaii.gov/dlnr/dar/pubs/ulua01.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>屬肉食性，利用伸縮的嘴，在珊瑚礁吸食小型無脊椎動物。<ref name="Heemstra">{{cite book|last=Heemstra|first=P.C.|title=Coastal Fishes of Southern Africa|url=https://archive.org/details/coastalfishessou00heem|year=2004|publisher=NISC Pty Ltd|isbn=9781920033019|pages=[https://archive.org/details/coastalfishessou00heem/page/488 488]|author2=Heemstra, E.}}</ref>在夏威夷，繁殖期發生在2月下旬至10月上旬，從4月下旬到9月上旬達到高峰<ref name=WatsonLeis>{{cite journal|last=Watson|first=W.|author2=Leis, J.M.|title=Ichthyoplankton of Kaneohe Bay, Hawaii: A one-year study of the fish eggs and larvae|journal=University of Hawaii Sea Grant College Program Technical Reports|year=1974|volume=UNIHI-SEAGRANT-TR-75-01}}</ref>；在[[波斯灣|波斯灣]]南部的[[印度洋|印度洋]]，繁殖期發生在4月和5月。<ref name="assess">{{cite journal|last1=Grandcourt|first1=E.M.|author2=T.Z. Al Abdessalaam|author3=F. Francis|author4=A. Al Shamsi|year=2004|title=Population biology and assessment of representatives of the family Carangidae ''Carangoides bajad'' and ''Gnathanodon speciosus'' (Forsskal, 1775), in the Southern Arabian Gulf|journal=Fisheries Research|volume=69|issue=3|pages=331–341|doi=10.1016/j.fishres.2004.06.008}}<!--| accessdate =2008-08-02 --></ref>

== 經濟利用 ==
[[File:Gnathanodon_speciosus_Prague_2011_1.jpg|thumb]]的水族館]]
本魚自古以來都被當成食用魚，<ref>{{cite book | last = Potts | first = D.T. | title = Before the Emirates: an Archaeological and Historical Account of Developments in the Region c. 5000 BC to 676 AD in ''Perspectives on the United Arab Emirates'' | year = 1997 | pages = 28–69 | url = http://uaeinteract.com/uaeint_misc/pdf/perspectives/02.pdf | doi =  | id =  | isbn =  | access-date = 2012-06-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120717040537/http://www.uaeinteract.com/uaeint_misc/pdf/perspectives/02.pdf | archive-date = 2012-07-17 | dead-url = yes | df =  }}</ref>本種仍然在太平洋群島使用許多傳統方法捕撈，當它遷移到較淺的水域時，將其捕獲。在較大的商業規模上，通常使用刺網和其他手工捕魚方法捕獲。西澳大利亞州的記錄表明，2010年商業漁業的黃金價格為3.3噸，<ref>{{cite journal|author=Department of Fisheries|journal=State of the Fisheries and Aquatic Resources Report|year=2011|volume=2010/11|url=http://www.fish.wa.gov.au/Documents/SOFAR/state_of_the_fisheries_2010-11.pdf|accessdate=30 June 2012|editor1=Fletcher, W.J.|editor2=Santoro, K.|issn=1838-4161|title=存档副本|archive-date=2014-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140903214035/http://www.fish.wa.gov.au/Documents/sofar/state_of_the_fisheries_2010-11.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>而昆士蘭州的漁獲量在1988年至2005年間波動在0.6至5.9噸之間。<ref>{{cite web|last=Department of Agriculture, Fisheries and Forestry|title=Coastal Habitat Resources Information System|url=http://chrisweb.dpi.qld.gov.au/CHRIS/|publisher=The State of Queensland|accessdate=30 June 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120725014325/http://chrisweb.dpi.qld.gov.au/CHRIS/|archivedate=25 July 2012|df=}}</ref>2000年至2010年，糧農組織記錄的全球捕撈量從1187噸到3475噸不等。新加坡、台灣、馬來西亞和印度尼西亞等則用籠養養殖。<ref name=Feng>{{cite journal|last=Feng|first=F. |author2=L.C. Lo |author3=G. Lin |author4=Z.Y. Zhu |author5=G.H. Yue|title=Isolation and characterization of microsatellites in a marine food fish species, golden trevally ''Gnathanodon specious''|journal=Molecular Ecology Notes|year=2005|volume=5|issue=4|pages=760–761|doi=10.1111/j.1471-8286.2005.01055.x}}</ref>另外由於本種色澤鮮艷而且攻擊力不強，在水族箱裡又很溫馴，容易飼養。另外也可作為食用魚，適合各種烹飪方法。

